Source.Name: avr-gcc
Source.Summary: The GNU Embedded GCC for Arm
Source.Description: The GNU Embedded Toolchain for Arm is a ready-to-use, open source suite of tools for C, C++ and Assembly programming targeting Arm Cortex-M and Cortex-R family of processors. It includes the GNU Compiler (GCC) and is available free of charge directly from Arm for embedded software development on Windows, Linux and Mac OS X operating systems.
